"content": "<p>A pouch worn on the chest of the high priest.</p>\n<h2>The breastpiece was worn by the high priest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:5-Lev8:9\">LEV 8:5–8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15-Exod28:16\">EXO 28:15–28:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:29\">EXO 28:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:8-Exod39:9\">EXO 39:8–39:9</a></p>\n<h3>It was adorned with twelve precious stones</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:17-Exod28:21\">EXO 28:17–28:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:3-Exod25:7\">EXO 25:3–25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:10-Exod39:14\">EXO 39:10–39:14</a></p>\n<h3>It contained the Urim and Thummim</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:30\">EXO 28:30</a></strong> <em>The Urim and Thummim were used in decision-making.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:8\">LEV 8:8</a></p>\n<h3>It was attached to the ephod</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:22-Exod28:28\">EXO 28:22–28:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:15-Exod39:21\">EXO 39:15–39:21</a></p>",
